DESCRIPTION:This workshop will push you to rethink the way you’ve been ta
 ught and to explore new teaching theory and best practices based on the Be
 yond Hands-On model. Students will explore usable teaching tools that can 
 be modified for any classroom\, any trade\, and all types of learners. Ope
 n to any and all educators. Scholarships available from NPS Historic Prese
 rvation Training Center and Preservation Maryland’s Campaign for Histori
 c Trades.
SUMMARY:How to Teach - Trades Educator Training
URL;VALUE=URI:https://ce.sbwi.edu/s/courseoffering/0P0V400000047MHKAY
